descriptionHtml:

title: EatEasy - Order Food Online

creator: Eateasily Online JLT
descriptionHtml:
EatEasy is the official mobile app of EatEasy.ae - UAE's leading online food and grocery ordering website and mobile app founded in 2013. EatEasy app is now available on App Store for both iPhone and iPad. Online Ordering for food and grocery delivery has never been so easier!

Features:
Order food for delivery from 1500+ restaurants in UAE.
Grocery shopping from local groceries and supermarkets.
Available in all cities of UAE - Dubai, Abu Dhabi, Sharjah, Ajman, Al Ain, Ras Al Khaima, Fujairah and Umm Al Quwain.
View hundreds of restaurant menu with customer reviews, food images, and item descriptions.
Place an advance order for food and grocery delivery. Schedule a particular date and time to place an order.
Search and filter restaurants according to food type, cuisine, payment type, minimum order, delivery time, delivery fee and locations.
Explore exciting discounts, offers, and promotions from different restaurants.
Add special instructions on each food item or add comments to notify restaurant.
Save multiple addresses like home, office and other addresses to order quickly from different locations.
View restaurant images, food pictures and more.
Earn cashback on your every order to redeem free food from different restaurants.
Live chat with our support team.
Place a similar order from your last order.
Track the status of your placed order.

For any information, you may send us an email to support@eateasy.ae
descriptionShort: Online Food & Grocery for Delivery And Restaurant Dine In.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Thank you for using the EatEasy App.
To make our app better for you, we have added new features Dine-In discounts ( Codes), Gift Card, and Smart Meals in this version.
We have Improved the user experience across the app

descriptionHtml:
EatEasy is the official mobile app of EatEasy.ae - UAE's leading online food and grocery ordering website and mobile app founded in 2013. EatEasy app is now available on App Store for both iPhone and iPad. Online Ordering for food and grocery delivery has never been so easier!

Features:
Order food for delivery from 6000+ restaurants in UAE.
Grocery shopping from local groceries and supermarkets.
Available in all cities of UAE - Dubai, Abu Dhabi, Sharjah, Ajman, Al Ain, Ras Al Khaima, Fujairah and Umm Al Quwain.
View hundreds of restaurant menu with customer reviews, food images, and item descriptions.
Place an advance order for food and grocery delivery. Schedule a particular date and time to place an order.
Search and filter restaurants according to food type, cuisine, payment type, minimum order, delivery time, delivery fee and locations.
Explore exciting discounts, offers, and promotions from different restaurants.
Add special instructions on each food item or add comments to notify restaurant.
Save multiple addresses like home, office and other addresses to order quickly from different locations.
View restaurant images, food pictures and more.
Earn cashback on your every order to redeem free food from different restaurants.
Live chat with our support team.
Place a similar order from your last order.
Track the status of your placed order.

For any information, you may send us an email to support@eateasy.ae
